fields.description:
The current version of the iOS Admob module is very out of date. The current version is 7.66.0.

There are several big improvements that have happened over the last year that we need to have updated for the module as-well as a few bugs that were fixed for upcoming iOS 15. 

You can see all released notes here: https://developers.google.com/admob/ios/rel-notes
